{"id":7736,"date":"2021-10-14T09:55:36","date_gmt":"2021-10-14T02:55:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=7736"},"modified":"2023-11-22T12:45:06","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T05:45:06","slug":"second-homes-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/second-homes-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang phong ph\u00fa h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh, m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh kinh doanh s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 <strong>Second Home<\/strong> l\u1ea1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat N\u0110T. V\u1eady Second Home l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Second Home l\u1ea1i \u0111ang l\u00e0 xu th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <strong>Vinhome Land<\/strong> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-grand-park\/\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Vinhomes Grand Park<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Second Home l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Second home l\u00e0 B\u0110S ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c C\u0110T thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. N\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 th\u1ee9 hai cho c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i, k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng cho thu\u00ea trong th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u1edf.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7758\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7758\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7758 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-nhung-yeu-to-noi-bat-cua-second-home-1-163351252077760047476-0-68-865-1366-crop-1633512532099724919340.png\" alt=\"Second Home l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/533;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7758\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7758\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-nhung-yeu-to-noi-bat-cua-second-home-1-163351252077760047476-0-68-865-1366-crop-1633512532099724919340.png\" alt=\"Second Home l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7758\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Second Home l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c B\u0110S \u1edf c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 v\u1eeba cho thu\u00ea l\u1ea1i khi kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd 2020? S\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh second home ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 v\u00ec nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc giao \u0111\u1ea5t cho C\u0110T l\u00e0m d\u1ef1 \u00e1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7757 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-1400x788-1.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7757\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-1400x788-1.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh hay d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u00e2u d\u00e0i do d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i sao Second home l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 xu th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng Second home \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh n\u00ean nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 B\u0110S. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf Second home \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.\u00a0<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ee3i<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1ef1 \u00e1n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan t\u00e2m ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c N\u0110T b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c Second home hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0ng. Bao quanh n\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i khu v\u1ef1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, s\u00e2n bay, ch\u1ee3 hay c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7753 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/533;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7753\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c Second home \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n nh\u1eefng \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 Second home hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch \u1edf nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n, nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00fai non y\u00ean t\u0129nh,\u2026 V\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Second home khi ra m\u1eaft th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng feedback t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c N\u0110T c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o n\u00f3.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0o Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh Second home \u0111ang l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh B\u0110S \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a th\u00edch. Do \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Second home hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 ho\u1eb7c gi\u1edbi v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng khi h\u1ecd hay b\u1ecb c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7750\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7750\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7750 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau th\u00edch\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7750\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7750\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-la-gi-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau th\u00edch\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7750\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3nh quan c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu gi\u00f3 m\u00f9a thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng n\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh Second home r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng sinh l\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng sinh l\u1eddi cao<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Second home \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh B\u0110S c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sinh cao. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch v\u1ec1 ch\u1ed7 \u1edf c\u1ee7a C\u0110T v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho thu\u00ea khi kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng t\u1edbi. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c n\u00f3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap C\u0110T t\u00edch l\u0169y ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n cho m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n th\u00ec Second home c\u00f2n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. C\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang t\u01b0 v\u1edbi ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7745 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7745\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/grand-marina-sai-gon-ba-son-quan-1\/\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Grand Marina Saigon<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Second Home t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh Second Home th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t hot. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh B\u0110S n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu cho m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Second Home l\u00e0 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Second home g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ch\u00ednh<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i TP. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u1ed3n \u00e0o v\u00e0 kh\u00f3i b\u1ee5i.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c Second Home kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Covid-19, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng du l\u1ecbch c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed \u0111i l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao.\u00a0<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7744\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7744\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7744 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-1024x536-1.jpg\" alt=\"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o Second home\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/419;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7744\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7744\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-1024x536-1.jpg\" alt=\"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o Second home\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7744\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o Second home<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh d\u1ecbch b\u1ec7nh Covid v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, vi\u1ec7c \u0111i l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y bay kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3. C\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, g\u1ea7n, d\u1ec5 di chuy\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ebd h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng Second Home c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e2n c\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, TP.HCM.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Second Home c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1eadn k\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecbch b\u1ec7nh<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Second home ven bi\u1ec3n kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc, nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c m\u1ed9t doanh nghi\u1ec7p B\u0110S cho r\u1eb1ng, nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u1edf lu\u00f4n l\u1edbn l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u00f3 tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, B\u0110S ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ec1n kh\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi gi\u00f3 m\u00f9a, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Second Home ven bi\u1ec3n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a C\u0110T.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7743 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-2.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"514\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/514;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7743\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/second-home-2.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"514\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n Second Home t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ghi nh\u1eadn, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 Ph\u00fa Qu\u1ed1c, Nha Trang, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng,,\u2026 C\u00e1c N\u0110T c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1ea7n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Quy Nh\u01a1n, Tuy H\u00f2a, Ninh Thu\u1eadn,,\u2026\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a N\u0110T c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch, c\u1ef1 ly v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khu v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 B\u00e0 R\u1ecba \u2013 V\u0169ng T\u00e0u, Phan Thi\u1ebft \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a B\u0110S khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u1ec1 du l\u1ecbch l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n TP.HCM. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch th\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 giao \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u00f3ng\u201d.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u l\u00fd khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn v\u00e0 sinh l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a N\u0110T khi mua lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Th\u1eddi gian s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi B\u0110S ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e2u, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5t s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng. T\u00e2m l\u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e2u d\u00e0i h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7739 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/nha-second-home.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/533;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7739\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/nha-second-home.jpg\" alt=\"Second homes l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu 50 n\u0103m hay l\u00e2u d\u00e0i?\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li aria-level=\"1\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed\u00a0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho thu\u00ea kh\u00f4ng? B\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed B\u0110S \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, khu v\u1ef1c du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f4ng? Kh\u00e1ch du l\u1ecbch l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n cung ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a second home.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n C\u0110T \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00f3 cao kh\u00f4ng? Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m c\u00f3 c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng hay \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e3o h\u00f2a?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u1ebft! Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\"><strong>vinhomeland.com.vn<\/strong><\/a>, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1<strong> Second Homes<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c xung quanh. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hay kh\u00f4ng. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;7736&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&